; -- $3A-$3F  Status ailment icons (after Z in set 1) ------------------------[I]
; Same 6 FF5 ailments as RPGe, but pixel art redesigned in ff5c.
; $3A: rocket/crystal glyph   $3B: creature/frog
; $3C: robot/mech face        $3D: feather/wing
; $3E: pi symbol (custom)     $3F: skull-face
3A=[stone]
3B=[toad]
3C=[mini]
3D=[float]
3E=[poison]
3F=[zombie]

; -- $40-$4F  Icon row --------------------------------------------------------[?]
; $40: sunglasses face (redesigned darkness icon in ff5c).
; $41-$4F: unknown; likely redesigned battle/status icons.
40=[darkness]
41=[icon-41]
