; -- $94-$B0  Kerning ligature tiles ------------------------------------------[P/I]
; RPGe packed common letter pairs as 8x8 tiles for tighter text layout.
; ff5c adds 4 new ligatures at $A6-$A9 (were unused [?] in RPGe).
; Punctuation / symbols in this range unchanged.
94=il
95=it
